snippet.title: A look at Phantasy Star Collection (Saturn)
snippet.description:
Uploaded for some people whom I thought might be interested in this.
 
-------

WHY DIDN'T WE GET THIS!? ;-;

This collection contains the BEST ports of the Phantasy Star games I have seen. The only problems other than Sega giving us the middle finger and not giving us a European or American release are that PSII's drums sound funny and PSIV has this load time for bosses.

Also, holy shit, I just noticed my computer slowed down to hell during some parts, I apologize for that.
